data.description:
Look no further if you are looking for space and an entertaining home. This could be the house you have been looking for and located in the sought-after community of Citrus Hills.  Roof new 05/2021 & HVAC 10/2019.No social membership is required, and it is situated on 1 acre with vinyl fencing. Immerse yourself in luxury in this 5 bedroom with an office, 3 full bathrooms, a 3-car garage, a formal living area, a formal dining area as well as a family room with a gas fireplace. The gourmet kitchen has cherry cabinets, granite, a built-in oven and microwave, and a spacious pantry. The master suite is well-appointed with beautiful tray ceilings: his and Her closets, dual vanities, a step-in shower, and a jetted soak tub. There is a large outdoor living area adjoining the heated saltwater pool and a spa with a cascading waterfall. The family room, living room, and master bedroom are open to the outdoor living area and pool deck. This home features the desired open living concept with a split bedroom floor plan design.
additionally, the guest suite bedroom has a private bathroom. The 3rd and 4th bedrooms share a jack-and-jill bathroom. The 5th bedroom could easily be a flex room (craft room, playroom, sitting room, etc.)
This home is an entertainers paradise, Conveniently located with easy access to shopping, restaurants & medical. Just 70 minutes to Tampa. 10 miles to Crystal River, close to freshwater springs, lakes, rivers, and the gulf.  Call me today to arrange for a showing or any additional information and STOP DREAMING AND START LIVING THE DREAM (Very motivated Seller)
